{"tid":1604103,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢發到成身肌肉酸痛，行步路都痛果種","createTime":"2019-09-30T00:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:51:32.000Z","uid":313764,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9394b5b829642797ae87d1e3cf5cc3676245eba8","tid":1604103,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"成身肌肉好似扯到恆哂咁, 大動作少少都好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n特別係左腳大腿位置, 酸痛到連想舉起隻腳都冇力舉唔起咁樣<br />\n<br />\n頭先係床頭想起身起床尾拎野點知成個腳發唔到力失重心扑撚左向前<br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇咩方法可以緩和下咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf862244d7bd2e0e39860ca4a02f7eabfff5272","tid":1604103,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"係咪平時無做開運動？"},{"pid":"b616ca5122b70e29a83e8422b4d31015e755b93e","tid":1604103,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6cf862244d7bd2e0e39860ca4a02f7eabfff5272","tid":1604103,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"係咪平時無做開運動？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:01:42.000Z","msg":"本身有樣運動玩緊,一星期操3,4次<br />\n<br />\n不過依排忙2,3個月冇操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effadd7dc9d63f373a2dc9277b5c08c68149a328","tid":1604103,"uid":322304,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19e1b1ef1eb328aae784a66d7cc7fb2d03708e52","tid":1604103,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"effadd7dc9d63f373a2dc9277b5c08c68149a328","tid":1604103,"uid":322304,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5070e0a9df7b513aa27898ad8f572017b3710b3","tid":1604103,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:03:27.000Z","msg":"拉筋/ 按摩器震番鬆？"},{"pid":"9e65b34852c684c5a210a45cef023c7c0a24f07a","tid":1604103,"uid":313764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5070e0a9df7b513aa27898ad8f572017b3710b3","tid":1604103,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:03:27.000Z","msg":"拉筋/ 按摩器震番鬆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:06:04.000Z","msg":"有做d伸展動作, 不過好似未見效<br />\n<br />\n按摩器就無啦, 4千幾5千幾我拎黎買文具派比隊友仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a41b1facb341074b2fb453c8e965435250ad31f","tid":1604103,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"btw 我其實想問下有冇其他人都好似我咁樣<br />\n<br />\n定還是我真係太廢,係個別例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf5a9861ec67938b5afbd62b74f4b5e29cb2211","tid":1604103,"uid":124045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a41b1facb341074b2fb453c8e965435250ad31f","tid":1604103,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"btw 我其實想問下有冇其他人都好似我咁樣<br />\n<br />\n定還是我真係太廢,係個別例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"就係好奇發夢平時都好大機會做開運動<br />\n<br />\n全身性肌肉酸痛一係病<br />\n<br />\n一係就食得煙/煙加料多<br />\n<br />\n發夢都全身酸痛拉下筋試下先<br />\n<br />\n你知d大肚婆都成日訓訓下抽筋抽醒<br />\n<br />\n再按摩下肌肉試下先"},{"pid":"f39790af4311c586f8d26e8184c665ebb9190ec9","tid":1604103,"uid":69140,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"血癌"},{"pid":"5047117a2a2002650cb9eba0e5da43e3612902c8","tid":1604103,"uid":27167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"衝個熱水涼"},{"pid":"94f187637b760d5cbb692be83381e9fdfb9ceba0","tid":1604103,"uid":266874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"同問，我都係早幾日操太勁宜家肌肉酸痛。<br />\n希望聽日出到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7ea1ea35